<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>κυρίῳ μου υἱῷ Κολλ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ού</unclear>θῳ

    <lb n="2"/>Γερόντιος χαίρειν.

    <lb n="3"/>οἶδεν ὁ θεός, οὐδέποτε

    <lb n="4"/>ἠνώχλησα πραιπ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">οσ</unclear>ί-

    <lb n="5"/>τῳ διὰ ξενίας τῶν β<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>-

    <lb n="6"/>ηθῶν μου ἢ ναυτῶν

    <lb n="7"/>ἢ τροφίμων ἢ ἄλλου τι-

    <lb n="8"/>νὸς διαφέροντός μοι,

    <lb n="9"/>ἀλλὰ ἀφ᾽ οὗ οἱ Μαῦροι ἐ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">νθ</unclear>ά-

    <lb n="10"/>δε ἦσαν τοὺς <choice><corr>μητάτορας</corr><sic>μιτατορας</sic></choice>

    <lb n="11"/>τιμῶ καὶ ἀλύπους ποιῷ

    <lb n="12"/>καὶ οὐδέποτε ἀντιλέγου-

    <lb n="13"/>σί μοι. οἱ νῦν κατασταθέν-

    <lb n="14"/>τες, ζητηθέντες ὑπ᾽ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἐ</unclear>-

    <lb n="15"/>μοῦ πολλάκις καὶ εὑρε-

    <lb n="16"/>θέντες, οὐ κατηξίωσαν

    <lb n="17"/>ἐλθεῖν πρὸς ὑμᾶς ἀλλὰ

    <lb n="18"/>ἀπελθόντες εἰσβάλλου-

    <lb n="19"/>σι στρατιώτας εἰς τὰς δια-

    <lb n="20"/>φερούσας ἡμῖν ο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἰ</unclear>κίας. οὐ

    <lb n="21"/><subst><add place="inline">θέλω</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">θε<gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>ω</del></subst> οὖν οὐδὲ νῦν ἐν<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>-

    <lb n="22"/>χλῆσαι τῷ κυρίῳ μου τῷ

    <lb n="23"/>πραιποσίτῳ ἀλλὰ τιμῆ-

    <lb n="24"/>σαι τοὺς <choice><corr>μητάτορας</corr><sic>μιτατορας</sic></choice> καὶ τι-

    <lb n="25"/>μηθῆναι παρ᾽ αὐτῶν.

    <lb n="26"/>παρακαλῶ οὖν, κύριε υἱέ,

    <lb n="27"/>συμβούλευσον αὐτο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ῖ</unclear>ς ἐλ-

    <lb n="28"/>θεῖν πρὸς ἐμέ· ἄτοπον γάρ

    <lb n="29"/>ἐστιν ὑβρισθῆναι ἡμᾶς

    <lb n="30"/>οὐδέποτε ὑβρισθέντας ἐπὶ

    <lb n="31"/>τῶν ξένων, μάλιστα σοῦ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear>οῦ

    <lb n="32"/>υἱοῦ δομεστικοῦ ὄντος. οὐ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δυ</unclear>-

    <lb n="33"/>νηθεὶς δὲ ἐλθεῖν διὰ τὴν ἀνα-

    <lb n="34"/>χώρησιν γράφω. ἐρρῶσθαί σε

    <lb n="35"/>εὔχομαι πολλοῖ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ς</unclear> -

    <lb n="36"/>νοις, κύριε <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">υἱέ</unclear>.</ab></div><div n="meta.78667" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.78667" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="301" notAfter="400">IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.78667" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.78667" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">67</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">4628</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">78667</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">67</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">4628</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0181;67;4628" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.78667" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">Plate X</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.78667" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><geogName type="nome" cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchites</geogName>, <geogName type="ancientRegion" key="Aegyptus" cert="high" full="yes">Egypt</geogName></p></div><div n="meta.78667" type="figure" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><figure href="http://163.1.169.40/cgi-bin/library?e=d-000-00---0POxy--00-0-0-0prompt-10---4---Document---0-1l--1-en-50---20-about---001-001-1-0utfZz-8-00031-001-1-0utfZz-8-00&amp;a=d&amp;c=POxy&amp;cl=CL5.1.14&amp;d=HASH054216b1999